function Start()

	Hydra.ActorSetPowerEffectSize(idMarker, 4)
	Hydra.ActorPlayEffectGroup(idMarker, vfxCharge)
	Hydra.Wait(2)
	Hydra.ActorPlayEffectGroup(idMarker, vfxBurst)
	Hydra.ActorDelete(idMoteJar)
	Hydra.ActorDelete(idMarker)
	Hydra.EventSend("ExplodeVessel")

end
